  "1890630": {
    "name": "混沌台球",
    "steam_appid": 1890630,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >混沌台球是一款完全不需要任何击球技巧的类Rogue台球游戏，您将亲自操控主球移动，赚取分数赢得比赛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/ad72a799ad044cb5555dd88e09426dc4.avif?t=1772098843\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以在关卡商店购买种类繁多的球杆，它们会给主球附加强大的武器：例如让主球像机关枪一样扫射，丢出高爆手雷，或者召唤净化光束！每场战斗可装备多种球杆，发挥想象力，品尝花式横扫红球的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/7c14780633ee773a8028ebc16c6e5bac.poster.avif?t=1772098843\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/7c14780633ee773a8028ebc16c6e5bac.webm?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/7c14780633ee773a8028ebc16c6e5bac.mp4?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/acbe69a2e635faf9453864e0028d663c.avif?t=1772098843\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要撞到红球就可以削减其血量，击破红球就会获得分数。主球没有血量的概念，无需担心生存问题，只要主动出击，在时间结束前获得足够分数即可过关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/b4bc6d58d0996e1d24e1fbe1c37bb971.poster.avif?t=1772098843\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/b4bc6d58d0996e1d24e1fbe1c37bb971.webm?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/b4bc6d58d0996e1d24e1fbe1c37bb971.mp4?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/fcd6fc6db0447ac006e9387542e4cd4d.avif?t=1772098843\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了击破红球获得的基础分数，您还有一个倍率数值，最终目标分数为基础分与倍率的乘积。关卡商店会上架各种增加倍率的装备，这些装备生效方式各不相同，一旦达成条件，就会成倍放大您的基础分数，使您在不断增长的分数挑战前无往不利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分数进度条充满时会随机投下几颗彩球，您只需要靠近彩球，按下“击球”键，就可以自动将其击入球袋，无需调整角度。球袋中的彩球会提供倍率，彩球颜色满足一定的“球型”时，还会获得额外倍率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/bb9f2ff57e348e5d567fbb9866fbf0a9.poster.avif?t=1772098843\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/bb9f2ff57e348e5d567fbb9866fbf0a9.webm?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/bb9f2ff57e348e5d567fbb9866fbf0a9.mp4?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/5257c2c8b0ea520bf7ebde2c47a63a75.avif?t=1772098843\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些强力装备需要彩球达成某种序列才能激活，一旦激活，您的球杆会变成超级武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/fba7ecb1479f46780534b34435452046.poster.avif?t=1772098843\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/fba7ecb1479f46780534b34435452046.webm?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/fba7ecb1479f46780534b34435452046.mp4?t=1772098843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890630/extras/23afe75f6f6068fca4c5d411cf28dcaa.avif?t=1772098843\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将逐渐解锁150多种独特的球杆或装备，搭配出无尽想象的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了传统的白球，还有多种意想不到的奇特主球任你驱使。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当您的背包中满载了球杆和装备，球袋中摆好了最佳球型时，敬请放松身心，享受一场火力充足的视听盛筵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
